[
    {
        "text": "How to Colonize a New Planet.",
        "startTime": 3563,
        "endTime": 5388,
        "slowStartTime": 5495,
        "slowEndTime": 8307
    },
    {
        "text": "Now that scientists have discovered evidence of thousands of other planets,...",
        "startTime": 6267,
        "endTime": 9987,
        "slowStartTime": 9550,
        "slowEndTime": 15205
    },
    {
        "text": "...the next question is obviously, how can we colonize them?",
        "startTime": 10151,
        "endTime": 13364,
        "slowStartTime": 15376,
        "slowEndTime": 20271
    },
    {
        "text": "Keep these considerations in mind to become a colonial power of galactic proportion.",
        "startTime": 14109,
        "endTime": 18711,
        "slowStartTime": 21314,
        "slowEndTime": 28291
    },
    {
        "text": "You will need: a planet in the Goldilocks zone,...",
        "startTime": 19641,
        "endTime": 22774,
        "slowStartTime": 29611,
        "slowEndTime": 34386
    },
    {
        "text": "...speedy spaceships, outer space fertility,...",
        "startTime": 23883,
        "endTime": 26891,
        "slowStartTime": 35974,
        "slowEndTime": 40562
    },
    {
        "text": "...man - made biospheres and terraforming.",
        "startTime": 27663,
        "endTime": 30619,
        "slowStartTime": 41644,
        "slowEndTime": 46154
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 1: Target a planet in the so-called Goldilocks zone,...",
        "startTime": 31416,
        "endTime": 35241,
        "slowStartTime": 47274,
        "slowEndTime": 53086
    },
    {
        "text": "...close enough to a sun so temperatures are neither too hot nor too cold but just right.",
        "startTime": 35488,
        "endTime": 40291,
        "slowStartTime": 53382,
        "slowEndTime": 60662
    },
    {
        "text": "This ensures that water would be available in liquid form.",
        "startTime": 40876,
        "endTime": 43723,
        "slowStartTime": 61464,
        "slowEndTime": 65810
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 2: Figure out how to get there in this lifetime.",
        "startTime": 44231,
        "endTime": 47113,
        "slowStartTime": 66497,
        "slowEndTime": 70894
    },
    {
        "text": "Most planets are light-years away.",
        "startTime": 47549,
        "endTime": 49229,
        "slowStartTime": 71474,
        "slowEndTime": 74068
    },
    {
        "text": "Circumventing the speed of light would be a good start.",
        "startTime": 49776,
        "endTime": 52132,
        "slowStartTime": 74814,
        "slowEndTime": 78423
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 3: If possible, pick an uninhabited land.",
        "startTime": 52907,
        "endTime": 56347,
        "slowStartTime": 79511,
        "slowEndTime": 84745
    },
    {
        "text": "It's much easier to colonize a new planet without any alien life forms...",
        "startTime": 56837,
        "endTime": 60459,
        "slowStartTime": 85406,
        "slowEndTime": 90913
    },
    {
        "text": "...who could very well outsmart and overpower earthlings.",
        "startTime": 60529,
        "endTime": 63289,
        "slowStartTime": 90943,
        "slowEndTime": 95159
    },
    {
        "text": "Renowned astrophysicist Stephen Hawking said that alien life is likely.",
        "startTime": 64459,
        "endTime": 68602,
        "slowStartTime": 96838,
        "slowEndTime": 103128
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 4: Protect human fertilization.",
        "startTime": 69581,
        "endTime": 72391,
        "slowStartTime": 104521,
        "slowEndTime": 108811
    },
    {
        "text": "Scientists investigating the feasibility of colonizing Mars...",
        "startTime": 73152,
        "endTime": 76358,
        "slowStartTime": 109878,
        "slowEndTime": 114762
    },
    {
        "text": "...found that high levels of radiation in space would make pregnancy problematic.",
        "startTime": 76460,
        "endTime": 80537,
        "slowStartTime": 114840,
        "slowEndTime": 121031
    },
    {
        "text": "And negative population growth makes a planet pretty hard to colonize.",
        "startTime": 80837,
        "endTime": 84710,
        "slowStartTime": 121405,
        "slowEndTime": 127290
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 5: Build housing:...",
        "startTime": 85658,
        "endTime": 87409,
        "slowStartTime": 128637,
        "slowEndTime": 131339
    },
    {
        "text": "...man - made biospheres that allow people to survive on the new planet...",
        "startTime": 87902,
        "endTime": 91367,
        "slowStartTime": 132003,
        "slowEndTime": 137275
    },
    {
        "text": "...by providing closed ecological systems.",
        "startTime": 91463,
        "endTime": 93761,
        "slowStartTime": 137345,
        "slowEndTime": 140867
    },
    {
        "text": "Step 6: Start terraforming:...",
        "startTime": 94229,
        "endTime": 96117,
        "slowStartTime": 141493,
        "slowEndTime": 144401
    },
    {
        "text": "...changing the new planet's environment so earthlings can live outside their biospheres.",
        "startTime": 96519,
        "endTime": 100723,
        "slowStartTime": 144928,
        "slowEndTime": 151310
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, try not to pollute it so soon!",
        "startTime": 101141,
        "endTime": 103385,
        "slowStartTime": 151861,
        "slowEndTime": 155303
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you know?",
        "startTime": 104138,
        "endTime": 104660,
        "slowStartTime": 156357,
        "slowEndTime": 157215
    },
    {
        "text": "Scientists believe that as many as half the stars in our galaxy...",
        "startTime": 105132,
        "endTime": 108249,
        "slowStartTime": 157848,
        "slowEndTime": 162598
    },
    {
        "text": "...have planets that are two to ten times the size of Earth and may sustain life.",
        "startTime": 108345,
        "endTime": 112438,
        "slowStartTime": 162667,
        "slowEndTime": 168882
    }
]